title: #5 Paris Attacks and #FreeCommunityCollege Dummies
description: What kind of culture argues that it is because of the “grace of god” that a 14 year old girl can be legally married? One founded by a pedophile, that’s which one. Chris Ford, Gerald Morgan and a terrorist joined us for today’s podcast to break down the disgrace that is Allah. Tune in as we discuss the latest madness in the world… and, here’s a video with some show highlights to whet your appetite!
